  mplayer2-9999.ebuild:
  Allow enabling/disabling xvid decoding over xvid.

  03 Apr 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> mplayer2-2.0.ebuild,
  mplayer2-9999.ebuild:
  Drop local setting of version and rely on buildscript :)

  03 Apr 2011; Tomáš Chvátal <scarabeus@gentoo.org> mplayer2-2.0.ebuild,
  mplayer2-9999.ebuild:
